\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 121. A. brachylobus} DC.,{\i   Prodr. }{\b 2}: 285 (1825). Like {\b 120} but peduncles c. 1-1½ times as long as leaves; racemes 6-15 cm, elongate, lax; calyx 10-15 mm, the teeth 1/5-1/4 as long as tube; standard 18-26 mm.{\i   Krym, S.E. Russia, W. Kazakhstan}. Rs (K, E).
